* W04_arbno_zero — ARBNO matches zero times then literal succeeds
* Rung W04. ARBNO zero match: subject 'hello' matches ARBNO('xyz') (zero) then 'hello'.

        subject = 'hello'
        subject (ARBNO('xyz') 'hello')  :f(e001)
        OUTPUT = 'PASS W04/002: arbno zero match'   :(END)
e001    OUTPUT = 'FAIL W04/002: arbno zero should succeed'
END
